summary: The video shows a woman applying makeup to her eyebrows. She is initially pleased with the result, but then expresses disbelief, suggesting she is not happy with the final look.

categories.name: visual_quality
categories.feedback: The video is well-lit and in focus, making it easy to see the makeup application.

categories.name: audio_quality
